<item>
            <title>[LU-18475] Kernel 6.12 support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18475</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Kernel v6.12 support:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.12-rc1-3-g5f60d5f6bbc1&lt;br/&gt;
  move asm/unaligned.h to linux/unaligned.h&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.11-rc1-51-ga225800f322a&lt;br/&gt;
  fs: Convert aops-&amp;gt;write_end to take a folio&lt;br/&gt;
 Linux v6.11-rc1-52-g1da86618bdce&lt;br/&gt;
  fs: Convert aops-&amp;gt;write_begin to take a folio&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.11-rc4-27-g11068e0b64cb&lt;br/&gt;
   fs: remove f_version&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.11-rc6-86-g09022bc196d2&lt;br/&gt;
   mm: remove PG_error&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.11-rc6-233-g99f86bbda317&lt;br/&gt;
   mm: remove PageMlocked&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Linux v6.11-rc6-225-ge880034cf718&lt;br/&gt;
   mm: introduce page_mapcount_is_type()&lt;/p&gt;</description>
